data.description: Welcome to your beautiful home located on a 1+ acre cul-de-sac lot nestled among a park-like community full of mature oak trees providing plenty of shade and privacy. As you step inside the home, you will appreciate the soaring ceilings and beautiful hardwood floors as you make your way into your home office/sitting area. An abundance of natural light flows in through the numerous windows that line the back of the home overlooking your very own private paradise. A floor-to-ceiling stone fireplace sets the tone of the living room and provides a warm living space. The gourmet kitchen features a center island with a wood butcher block countertop, a six-burner gas cooktop, double ovens, microwave drawer, and warming drawer ready for a masterfully prepared meal for your holiday gatherings! The master bedroom features a relaxing en-suite with a large soaking tub and gorgeous views of the tree covered yard. Relax in your spacious and private outdoor living area while entertaining family and friends. The park-like yard features a fenced area for kids and pets, and includes a gardening shed and playhouse for kids. The yard continues beyond the fenced area with a wooded area that provides privacy and excellent viewing of wildlife to include deer and fox. This private paradise feels like it is miles away from civilization, yet is just around the corner to everything you need. Drop your boat or jet skis into Lake Georgetown in 5 minutes, ride your bike to Jim Hogg Park, hike the many trails around Lake Georgetown, or go shopping and enjoy great restaurants in just a few minutes from home. No HOA and very low tax rate.  *** New Class 4, impact resistant shingles scheduled for installation in December.
